title: Fantastic 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Rear Home in North Long Beach!
posting_body: ['Fantastic 2 Bedroom 2 Bath Rear Home in North Long Beach!', 'Property Address', '1231 E. South St. | Long Beach, CA 90805', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Offered By', 'Ernst and Haas Management Co.', 'Description', 'Now Leasing!!', 'A lovely 2 bedroom 1 bath detached rear home in a great North Long Beach location, just blocks from schools, stores, and public transit.', 'The home sits on a shared lot with a front house and has a shared yard and water is included.', 'The interior of this lovely unit opens to a spacious main living room, painted in a bright, modern white, and boasting tile flooring, blinds, and connects to a nicely sized kitchen area with ample kitchen cabinets, and counters, and an in-kitchen dining area.', 'The floor plan includes 2 nicely sized bedrooms, each with tile flooring and blinds, and each has a separate bathroom.', 'The home also includes an attached 1-car garage.', 'For more information on this or any other available property, please contact Ernst & Haas Management at', 'show contact info', ', or visit us online at <URL> and apply today.', 'TO QUALIFY:', '• Credit score must be no less than 600', '• Monthly gross income to qualify must be 2 ½ times the rent', '• We do not accept past evictions, judgments, or collections from a management company or landlord', '• Renter’s Insurance is required.', 'Proof of coverage must be provided upon the signing of your lease.', '*Note - See selection criteria for a detailed list of qualifications on our website at <URL>', 'PLEASE BE AWARE OF RENTAL SCAMS:', 'We caution all applicants to be diligent in researching the legitimacy of any potential rental listing.', 'All deposits, rents, and rental agreements\xa0are ONLY executed at Ernst & Haas Management, 4120 Atlantic Ave., Long Beach, CA.', 'If you are being asked to fill out a third-party application or are being asked to pay cash or send money via an App, Western Union, Money-Gram, or Prepaid Visa card,\xa0STOP\xa0these\xa0are signs of rental listing scams used to defraud applicants.', 'Ernst and Haas Management Co.', 'DRE License #01251870', '*ALL INFORMATION DEEMED ACCURATE BUT NOT GUARANTEED.', 'APPLIANCES ARE PROVIDED AS A COURTESY AND ARE NOT MANDATORY TO THE LEASE.', 'TERMS ARE SUBJECT TO CHANGE WITHOUT NOTICE.', 'Amenities', 'Stove', 'Water Paid', '1 Car Attached Garage', 'Shared Yard', 'Blinds', 'Sorry No Pets', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/2.0BA', 'Square Feet: 900', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,395.00', 'Available: 08/05/2022', 'Application Fee: $45.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,400.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats not allowed', 'Dogs not allowed']
